                  "pageTitle": "Cat's Eye",
                  "pageId": 1016527,
                  "revisionId": 2793263,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "Despite its description, Cat's Eye adds 60 percentage points to a weapon's critical chance after other bonuses, similar to Arcane Avenger . This type of buff is commonly referred to as an absolute or final bonus."
                }
              },
              {
                "reviewStatus": "draft",
                "provenance": {
                  "source": "local-wiki-sqlite",
                  "pageTitle": "Cat's Eye",
                  "pageId": 1016527,
                  "revisionId": 2793263,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "Cat's Eye stacks additively with other percentage point bonuses, such as Arcane Avenger . For example, an Atterax with a max rank True Steel , Blood Rush at a 4.0x combo multiplier, Cat's Eye , and Arcane Avenger will have a 25% × (1 + 120% + 40%×(4 - 1)) + 60% + 45% = 190% critical chance."
                }
              },
              {
                "reviewStatus": "draft",
                "provenance": {
                  "source": "local-wiki-sqlite",
                  "pageTitle": "Cat's Eye",
                  "pageId": 1016527,
                  "revisionId": 2793263,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "Highly effective with weapons with high critical damage multipliers."
                }
              },
              {
                "reviewStatus": "draft",
                "provenance": {
                  "source": "local-wiki-sqlite",
                  "pageTitle": "Cat's Eye",
                  "pageId": 1016527,
                  "revisionId": 2793263,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "Emplaced turrets (i.e. the Grineer Rampart ) gain the ability to critically strike while under the effect of Cat's Eye."
                }
              },
              {
                "reviewStatus": "draft",
                "provenance": {
                  "source": "local-wiki-sqlite",
                  "pageTitle": "Cat's Eye",
                  "pageId": 1016527,
                  "revisionId": 2793263,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "While this also applies to weapons that cannot critically strike, these weapons often have a critical multiplier of 1.0x which yields no change in damage dealt."
                }
              },
              {
                "reviewStatus": "draft",
                "provenance": {
                  "source": "local-wiki-sqlite",
                  "pageTitle": "Cat's Eye",
                  "pageId": 1016527,
                  "revisionId": 2793263,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "Multiple instances of Cat's Eye do not stack."
                }
              },
              {
