                  "pageId": 1016527,
                  "revisionId": 2793263,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "The cooldown of 20 seconds starts when Cat's Eye's duration stops. This leads to an effective uptime of 10 ÷ (10 + 20) = 33.33% ."
                }
              },
